==== How to use ===

In your controller file, add this lines

var IslamicDate = require('../lib/IslamicDate');

Somewhere in your event handler, add this

var adjustment = -2;
var islamicDate = new IslamicDate.IslamicDate();

console.log(islamicDate.getIslamicDate(adjustment));

